# .test-ignore
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Glob patterns for UI files that should NOT require unit test coverage.
# The pre-commit hook (scripts/hooks/pre-commit) reads this file.
#
# Syntax:
#   - One pattern per line
#   - Patterns are matched against the repo-relative file path using bash globs
#   - Lines starting with # are comments
#   - Blank lines are ignored
#
# Examples:
#   web/src/components/icons/*          skip an entire directory
#   web/src/views/LegacyView.vue        skip a single file
#   web/src/**/SkipMe.ts                skip by filename anywhere under web/src
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Icon components ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SVG-wrapper icon components have no logic to test
web/src/components/icons/*

# ── Cloud / enterprise feature guards ────────────────────────────────────────
# Top-level cloud/enterprise wrappers are tested via integration tests
web/src/cloud/index.ts
web/src/enterprise/index.ts

# ── Build / environment config ────────────────────────────────────────────────
web/src/aws-exports.ts
web/src/main.ts

# ── Re-export barrel files ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Pure index.ts re-exports are caught by the heuristic but list explicit ones here
# web/src/stores/index.ts

# ── Known large files with integration-test coverage only ────────────────────
# Uncomment and add files your team has agreed to skip:
# web/src/views/HomeView.vue
